# =========================================
# WaBro V2 — Deployment Configuration
# =========================================
# Used by Coolify on Hetzner Cloud

# --- Domain & SSL ---
# Primary: wabro.propai.live
# SSL: Let's Encrypt (auto-renewed by Coolify/Traefik)
# DNS: A record -> Hetzner server IP

# --- Build Commands ---
# Coolify auto-detects Dockerfile
# No build command needed — static web server

# --- Start Command ---
# docker run -p ${PORT:-8000}:8000 wabro-landing:latest

# --- Health Check (Coolify default) ---
# curl -f http://localhost:8000/ || exit 1

# --- Post-Deploy ---
# Coolify handles zero-downtime rolling updates